	<h1 class="title">呀，麦咖啡的杯子都成表白神器了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">谢宇程阳</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-13 10:29:04 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/20607/medium/20607.jpg?1452594030" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


